    {
        "content": "<p>At some point this instance seems to have one of its functions changed so that its result type points directly to a record field (which is illegal) instead of pointing to a type.</p>",
        "id": 348447487,
        "sender_full_name": "Ryan Levick (rylev)",
        "timestamp": 1681216162
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>This particular instance is not itself being composed (i.e., it should be fine for the composer to just round trip).</p>",
